      • exists

        boolean exists(String name)
        Returns true if the icon theme contains a mapping for the specified iconName.
        Parameters:
        iconName - The key to check if it has been registered in this IconTheme
        Returns:
        true if this IconTheme contains iconName, false otherwise.

      • get

        ImageIcon get(String iconName)
        Gets the ImageIcon associated with the provided name, if the name is present in the theme. If the icon not exists try to return a icon with name "no-icon" or returns null if this not exists.
        Parameters:
        name - The name whose associated icon is to be retrieved
        Returns:
        The icon associated with the provided name

      • setDescription

        void setDescription(String description)
        Sets the theme description. It should be a short description (around 20-30 words), including the highlights of the theme, the author and maybe its email address or a link the the theme's homepage.

      • registerDefault

        void registerDefault(String provider,
                   String group,
                   String name,
                   ImageIcon icon,
                   URL resource)
                     throws IllegalArgumentException
        Register a icon in the theme. The parameter icon can be null if the resource is specified. The parameter resource can be null if the icon is specified. Plugin and group can be null.
        Parameters:
        provider - name of the icon
        group - name for the icon.
        name - of icon
        icon, - can be nulll if the resource is specified.
        resource, - resource of the icon, usualy and url to the icon.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if name is null/empty or icon/resource are null
